        "authorId" : "dc1cfabe-d5ff-47d1-862d-2ac96e9bd158",
        "body" : "Unfortunately it is:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/nexpy/nexusformat/blob/e1e6689b1651b8b7217158528336b80d8f126113/setup.py#L1-L16\r\n\r\nNot sure why though since it isn't actually used further on in the script AFAICT",
